data.title: Biography
data.meta_description: Ho-Yan Mok. Actress: San ging hap lui. Ho-Yan Mok was born on 8 October 1969 in Hong Kong, British Crown Colony. She is an actress, known for San ging hap lui (2005), Ni ge mie ye chang (1997) and Tor cheung si je (1998). She has been married to Alex Fong since 7 June 2008. They have one child.
